    title="About the film"
    subtitle='A film by producer and director Marina Hitt tells the story of a Soviet immigrant who arrived in the USA in the late 70s with an infant in arms and 70 dollars to his name. Years later, thanks to the support of his wife, he earned a multi-million dollar fortune and created a "glass" empire that services the skyscrapers of Manhattan.'
  >
    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-gray-900"></div>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="image">
      <div class="relative h-0 pb-[56.25%]">
